      This idea simply remind us why our government is in the shape it is today, a government filled with officials not bright enough to comprehend complex ideas without the need of pop-up pictures and coloring areas... I mean visual recordings.<br/><br/>I do not completely disregard the idea, I think it's a very good one for what it's worth, which I hope it's close to free. A digital graphic or 3D model artist could, however create a more visually and interactive experience and present complex ideas that can be understood more fluently by a broader audience. 

                  
    </td>
